News and release history of the Open Input library

------------------------------------------------------------------------

12.09.2006 makob -- Version 0.2.3
    * Almost a year since last version!
    * Major documentation updates and additions
    * Many bugfixes
    * Partial DirectInput driver (disabled per default)

22.09.2005 makob -- Version 0.2.2
    * Microsoft Visual C compiler support
    * Support is now: GNU/Linux, mingw, MSVC
    * Major bugfixes all around

15.09.2005 makob -- Version 0.2.1
    * Some "brown paper hat" fixes for GNU/Linux building

15.09.2005 makob -- Version 0.2.0
    * Drivers: X11, posix signal, Linux joystick and Win32
    * Keyboard, mouse and joystick managers

17.06.2005 makob -- Version 0.0.1
    * Project startup
